title: Kannu Korts
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Italian, Buffet, Salad bar, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Restaurant/bar offers a wide selection of vegetarian dishes, of which some are vegan or can be made vegan. Vegetarian buffet Mon-Sun 12-7pm with vegan choices. Located outside of the city centre, reachable by bus 20 and 24A (bus stop Kassi).Atmosphere is children friendly and spacious with Wi-Fi access. Free parking zone. English spoken.
